BUG-11: Timezone Helper is Broken

Severity: Critical

Environment: Windows 11, Chrome Browser

Steps to Reproduce (STR):

1)Navigate to the "Timezone Helper."

2)Enter any valid local date and time.

3)Select any "Target Zone."

4)Click "Convert."

Expected Result: The converted date and time should be displayed correctly for the selected target timezone.

Actual Result: The app produces an incorrect result and fails to change the timezone, leaving the output in "India Standard Time."

Evidence:
 ![Screenshot showing Timezone Helper is Broken](evidence\bug-11-timezone-broken.png)